import { Repository } from 'typeorm';
import { GetDocumentsInput } from './dto/get-documents.input';
import { UpdateDocumentInput } from './dto/update-document.dto';
import { UploadDocumentInput } from './dto/upload-document.dto';
import { DocumentEntity } from './entities/document.entity';
export declare class DocumentService {
    private documentRepository;
    constructor(documentRepository: Repository<DocumentEntity>);
    countDocument(idUser: string | null, idProject: string | null, searchDocumentsInput: string): Promise<number>;
    updateDocument(idUser: string, updateDocumentInput: UpdateDocumentInput): Promise<{
        project: import("../project/entities/project.entity").Project;
        idDocument: string;
        documentName: string;
        pathDocument: string;
        description?: string;
        createdAt: Date;
        updatedAt: Date;
    }>;
    findAll(idUser?: string | null, idProject?: string | null, optionsInput?: GetDocumentsInput<DocumentEntity>): Promise<DocumentEntity[]>;
    getByIdProject(idProject: string): Promise<DocumentEntity[]>;
    deleteByIdProject(idProject: string): Promise<void>;
    deleteById(idUser: string, idDocument: string): Promise<DocumentEntity>;
    private saveDocumentToDir;
    createDocument(uploadDocumentInput: UploadDocumentInput): Promise<DocumentEntity>;
}
